{"text_id":213860,"tokens":["In"," recent"," years",","," the"," use"," of"," cell"," phones"," in"," schools"," has"," become"," a"," contentious"," issue","."," While"," some"," argue"," that"," cell"," phones"," are"," essential"," tools"," for"," communication"," and"," emergency"," situations",","," others"," maintain"," that"," the"," use"," of"," cell"," phones"," in"," schools"," should"," be"," prohibited"," due"," to"," the"," potential"," for"," cheating",","," distraction"," from"," learning",","," and"," misuse"," of"," technology",".","\n\n","Firstly",","," cell"," phones"," enable"," students"," to"," cheat"," on"," exams"," and"," quizzes",","," which"," undermines"," the"," integrity"," of"," the"," educational"," system","."," Students"," can"," easily"," access"," notes",","," textbooks",","," and"," the"," internet"," during"," tests",","," giving"," them"," an"," unfair"," advantage"," over"," those"," who"," do"," not"," cheat","."," This"," not"," only"," dis","rupts"," the"," academic"," environment"," but"," also"," dist","orts"," the"," grading"," system",".","\n\n","Secondly",","," cell"," phones"," can"," be"," a"," significant"," distraction"," in"," the"," classroom","."," Students"," may"," use"," their"," phones"," to"," play"," games",","," text",","," or"," browse"," the"," internet"," during"," lessons","."," This"," behavior"," is"," not"," only"," disrespectful"," to"," teachers"," and"," other"," students"," but"," also"," hinders"," learning","."," Research"," has"," shown"," that"," students"," who"," use"," cell"," phones"," in"," class"," score"," lower"," on"," exams"," than"," those"," who"," do"," not"," use"," them","."," Moreover",","," cell"," phone"," usage"," in"," the"," classroom"," can"," create"," a"," competitive"," and"," distracting"," environment",","," affecting"," the"," learning"," of"," all"," students",".","\n\n","Lastly",","," cell"," phones"," can"," be"," misused"," for"," bullying",","," cyber","bull